 data are found to be\nconsistent with the profiles obtained with the radial velocity data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2006 14:13:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2006 11:49:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
